            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"馬來西亞令吉升至2018年以來最高水平 受AI、經濟成長樂觀情緒提振\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/j1wcV.hz86cI5RdFnAu4lw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/d42c8980-fa58-11f0-bfbf-d38925efe1d5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">馬來西亞令吉升至2018年以來最高水平 受AI、經濟成長樂觀情緒提振</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E4%BB%A4%E5%90%89%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B32018%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3-%E5%8F%97ai-%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF-003845382.html",
